<item>
            <title>[LU-19145] kernel update [RHEL 8.10 4.18.0-553.58.1.el8_10]</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19145</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Security Fix(es):&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: cifs: fix double free race when mount fails in cifs_get_root() (CVE-2022-48919)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: security/keys: fix slab-out-of-bounds in key_task_permission (CVE-2024-50301)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: idpf: fix idpf_vc_core_init error path (CVE-2024-53064)&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;kernel: ndisc: use RCU protection in ndisc_alloc_skb() (CVE-2025-21764)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHSA-2025:9580&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://access.redhat.com/errata/product/479/ver=/rhel---8/x86_64/RHSA-2025:9580&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
